index=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 29, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gtt1665702780356.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gtt1665702780356.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gtt1665702780356.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gtt1665702780356\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Sort Objects and\n      Properties</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__sort_objects_and_properties_16501\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can sort items listed in the Uniface IDE by clicking the sort icon above the column header.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__topic_d3776e1_d3777e1_d3778e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__p_d3779e1_d3780e1_d3781e1\">The Sort icon is displayed above selected columns in the U-Bar, Resource Browser, Properties Inspector, and Structure panes. The appearance of the icon reflects the current sort order.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><img alt=\"Original Order Icon is a small dot\" class=\"image\" height=\"38\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__image_djf_tyq_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/iconsortoriginal.png?_LANG=enus\" width=\"56\"/> Original order</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><img alt=\"Descending Order Icon is a small down arrow\" class=\"image\" height=\"40\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__image_jkf_vyq_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/iconsortdesc.png?_LANG=enus\" width=\"60\"/> Descending order</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><img alt=\"Ascending Order Icon is a small up arrow\" class=\"image\" height=\"40\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__image_hqm_xyq_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/iconsortasc.png?_LANG=enus\" width=\"56\"/> Ascending order </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__section_w8460ab1b5b5_w8461ab1b5_w8462ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gtt1665702780356__p_d3782e1_d3783e1_d3784e1\">To change the sort order, click the icon until the items are sorted in your preferred order.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Sort Objects and Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 29, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sort Objects and Properties You can sort items listed in the Uniface IDE by clicking the sort icon above the column header. The Sort icon is displayed above selected columns in the U-Bar, Resource Browser, Properties Inspector, and Structure panes. The appearance of the icon reflects the current sort order. Original order Descending order Ascending order To change the sort order, click the icon until the items are sorted in your preferred order. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}